Grammar csharp

start ::=

  • compilation_unit
  • (used in )
  • May be empty
  • MayStartWith: extern namespace using [ partial class struct interface enum delegate new public protected internal private abstract sealed static unsafe
  • MayBeFollowedBy:

compilation_unit ::=

  • extern_alias_directive* using_directive* global_attributes? namespace_member_declaration*
  • (Spec: Compilation units)
  • (used in start)
  • May be empty
  • MayStartWith: extern namespace using [ partial class struct interface enum delegate new public protected internal private abstract sealed static unsafe
  • MayBeFollowedBy:

namespace_declaration ::=

  • namespace qualified_identifier namespace_body ;?
  • (Spec: Namespace declarations)
  • (used in namespace_member_declaration)
  • Never empty
  • MayStartWith: namespace
  • MayBeFollowedBy: namespace partial class struct interface enum delegate new public protected internal private abstract sealed static [ unsafe }

qualified_identifier ::=

  • identifier ( . identifier )*
  • (Spec: Namespace declarations)
  • (used in namespace_declaration)
  • Never empty
  • MayStartWith: @ <An identifier_or_keyword that is not a keyword>
  • MayBeFollowedBy: {

namespace_body ::=

  • { extern_alias_directive* using_directive* namespace_member_declaration* }
  • (Spec: Namespace declarations)
  • (used in namespace_declaration)
  • Never empty
  • MayStartWith: {
  • MayBeFollowedBy: ; namespace partial class struct interface enum delegate new public protected internal private abstract sealed static [ unsafe }

extern_alias_directive ::=

  • extern alias identifier ;
  • (Spec: Extern aliases)
  • (used in compilation_unit namespace_body)
  • Never empty
  • MayStartWith: extern
  • MayBeFollowedBy: namespace partial class struct interface enum delegate new public protected internal private abstract sealed static [ unsafe using extern }

using_directive ::=

  • using_alias_directive
  • using_namespace_directive
  • using_static_directive
  • (Spec: Using directives)
  • (used in compilation_unit namespace_body)
  • Never empty
  • MayStartWith: using
  • MayBeFollowedBy: namespace partial class struct interface enum delegate new public protected internal private abstract sealed static [ unsafe using }

using_alias_directive ::=

  • using identifier = namespace_or_type_name ;
  • (Spec: Using alias directives)
  • (used in using_directive)
  • Never empty
  • MayStartWith: using
  • MayBeFollowedBy: namespace partial class struct interface enum delegate new public protected internal private abstract sealed static [ unsafe using }

using_namespace_directive ::=

  • using namespace_name ;
  • (Spec: Using namespace directives)
  • (used in using_directive)
  • Never empty
  • MayStartWith: using
  • MayBeFollowedBy: namespace partial class struct interface enum delegate new public protected internal private abstract sealed static [ unsafe using }

using_static_directive ::=

  • using static type_name ;
  • (Spec: Using static directives)
  • (used in using_directive)
  • Never empty
  • MayStartWith: using
  • MayBeFollowedBy: namespace partial class struct interface enum delegate new public protected internal private abstract sealed static [ unsafe using }

namespace_member_declaration ::=

  • namespace_declaration
  • type_declaration
  • (Spec: Namespace members)
  • (used in compilation_unit namespace_body)
  • Never empty
  • MayStartWith: namespace partial class struct interface enum delegate new public protected internal private abstract sealed static [ unsafe
  • MayBeFollowedBy: namespace partial class struct interface enum delegate new public protected internal private abstract sealed static [ unsafe }

type_declaration ::=

  • class_declaration
  • struct_declaration
  • interface_declaration
  • enum_declaration
  • delegate_declaration
  • (Spec: Type declarations)
  • (used in namespace_member_declaration class_member_declaration struct_member_declaration)
  • Never empty
  • MayStartWith: partial class struct interface enum delegate new public protected internal private abstract sealed static [ unsafe
  • MayBeFollowedBy: namespace partial class struct interface enum delegate new public protected internal private abstract sealed static [ unsafe } const event extern ~ readonly volatile virtual override object dynamic string @ void bool <An identifier_or_keyword that is not a keyword> decimal sbyte byte short ushort int uint long ulong char float double fixed

qualified_alias_member ::=

  • identifier :: identifier type_argument_list?
  • (Spec: Namespace alias qualifiers)
  • (used in namespace_or_type_name member_access named_entity_target)
  • Never empty
  • MayStartWith: @ <An identifier_or_keyword that is not a keyword>
  • MayBeFollowedBy: ; . ] , ( ? [ > { ) < <= >= is @ <An identifier_or_keyword that is not a keyword> this operator * where as == => != & ^ | && || ?? } <Any character except " (U+0022), : (U+003A), { (U+007B) and } (U+007D)> : from select group let join orderby equals on into ascending descending by const event extern ~ partial class struct interface enum delegate new public protected internal private static readonly volatile virtual sealed override abstract unsafe object dynamic string void bool decimal sbyte byte short ushort int uint long ulong char float double fixed

  • internal
  • private
  • protected internal
  • internal protected
  • (Spec: Accessors)
  • (used in get_accessor_declaration set_accessor_declaration)
  • Never empty
  • MayStartWith: protected internal private
  • MayBeFollowedBy: get set

  • block
  • ;

  • (used in get_accessor_declaration set_accessor_declaration)
  • Never empty
  • MayStartWith: { ;
  • MayBeFollowedBy: } set protected internal private [ get
